data/
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
*.jsonl

## IDE / OS
.vs/
.vscode/
*.user
*.suo
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

## .NET publish
*.exe
*.pdb
*.deps.json
*.runtimeconfig.json
